title: Intro to Fix & Flip and Rental Income Property Analysis
description:
Description

Are you sick and tired of real estate “systems” that turn out to just be a hard sell for another “system”?Tired of “no money down get rich like me” real estate investing “secrets” from real estate “gurus” that leave you filled with nothing but marketing fluff?Do you just want to know what REAL real estate investment analysis is all about?If you want to learn the fundamentals of real estate investing and how to actually evaluate investment opportunities the way professional investors do, keep reading.I can’t promise I’ll help you get rich, own a yacht and two Ferraris.But I can teach you some serious real estate investment analysis techniques.After getting my MBA from Stanford, I worked on over $400M in real estate deals.And I took what I learned from that and put all of it in this course.


Who is the target audience?

    Newbies to real estate investing
    Those who are serious about investing in fix & flips or rental income properties
    Someone who wants to build a solid foundation for their real estate investing knowledge

Requirements

    Have Microsoft Excel 2007 or Newer
